{"tid":504723,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Nokia 9 搶閘現身","createTime":"2017-12-20T10:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T14:11:55.000Z","uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1d91b1928388ed2e2d7a961738a1f33474b4237f","tid":504723,"uid":66607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"尚有 10 日左右 2017 年就告一段落，不少手機迷都已經將目光放在明年會發表的旗艦之上。雖然 Samsung Galaxy S9 和 S9+ 據說要到明年 2 月才發表，但 1 月還是會有旗艦級新機登場，其中一部相信是 HMD Global 推出的 Nokia 9。<br />\n<br />\n傳聞指 Nokia 會在明年 1 月 19 日於大陸發表 Nokia 9，日前有大陸網站就刊登了宣稱是 Nokia 9 的真機圖片。可以見到機身為藍色，正面採用沒有 Home 按鍵的全面屏設計，左右兩邊幾乎是無邊框，上下則極窄。可以見到機頂有兩枚前置鏡頭，暗示 Nokia 9 將採用前後雙鏡頭的配置。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4529/209749/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4529%2F209749%2F1%2F&d=Xd07no4XomrZPhsnyzK6aqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=60dc1e4e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4529/209749/1/</a>"},{"pid":"42c9c72de3c054bd4bce5ebb64f7a5ff4dc1a3f9","tid":504723,"uid":37688,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"如果係用835都當係舊旗艦嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搶乜閘呀"},{"pid":"9ff1546ab56fd057aee33a5dec7da706fdfb576b","tid":504723,"uid":136431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"係咪冇Jack 頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f302b91021e2ea6f3a986a5fa27e915c9ac33b6","tid":504723,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8f0f11b16aaff09ea4b9d132adb8dd3836cbf57","tid":504723,"uid":25612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T14:11:55.000Z","msg":"Nokia 個UI係鬼咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}